---
import DaySidebar from "../../components/DaySidebar.astro";
import Main from "../../components/Main.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Days";
const navItems = await Astro.glob("../../notes/*.md");
const subNavItems = await Astro.glob("../../notes/**/*.md");
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <DaySidebar slot="sidebar" navItems={navItems} subNavItems={subNavItems} />
  <Main title={title}>
    <h1>Day Overview</h1>
    <p>
      Join us for a 5-day intensive web development workshop, where you'll learn
      the fundamental building blocks of the web - HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
      This hands-on course is perfect for beginners who want to learn how to
      create and style web pages, as well as more experienced developers looking
      to refresh their skills.
    </p>
    <p>
      You'll work on real-world projects and receive one-on-one guidance from
      our expert instructors. By the end of the workshop, you'll have a solid
      understanding of how to use these powerful technologies to build
      professional-quality websites. Don't miss this opportunity to jumpstart
      your web development career! Sign up now.
    </p>
    <p>
      The goal of a web development workshop is to provide attendees with a
      strong foundation in web development concepts and techniques, as well as
      the practical skills needed to build and deploy functional,
      professional-quality websites.
    </p>
  </Main>
</Layout>
